===============
 Push Updates to Offline Clients
- Ensure clients are configured to receive updates from SEPM:
- In SEPM:
Policies > LiveUpdate > LiveUpdate Settings Policy
- Set source to:
"Use the default management server"
- Clients will receive updates during heartbeat communication with SEPM


